<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Chen's blog (Posts about mc)</title><link>http://blog.binchen.org/</link><description></description><atom:link href="http://blog.binchen.org/categories/mc.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 12 Sep 2020 03:02:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>The most important features of Midnight Commander (MC)</title><link>http://blog.binchen.org/posts/the-most-important-features-of-midnight-commander-mc/</link><dc:creator>Chen Bin</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Since I was a big fan of &lt;a href="http://www.ghisler.com"&gt;Total Commander (TC)&lt;/a&gt;, I priorize the MC's feature according to my TC's experience. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; Here is the list (C = Ctrl, M = Alt, S = Shift): &lt;/p&gt;&lt;table border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6" rules="groups" frame="hsides"&gt; &lt;caption&gt;&lt;/caption&gt; &lt;colgroup&gt;&lt;col class="left"&gt;&lt;col class="left"&gt;&lt;col class="left"&gt; &lt;/colgroup&gt; &lt;thead&gt; &lt;tr&gt;&lt;th scope="col" class="left"&gt;Feature&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th scope="col" class="left"&gt;MC&lt;/th&gt;&lt;th scope="col" class="left"&gt;TC&lt;/th&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/thead&gt; &lt;tbody&gt; &lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;Bookmark&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;C-\, then "New Entry"&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;C-D&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;Quick Search&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;C-s or M-s&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;C-M-first&lt;sub&gt;character&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;sub&gt;of&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;sub&gt;file&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;sub&gt;name&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;Find File&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;M-?&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;M-F7&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;Select Files by Pattern&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;+ (- will unselect files)&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;C-F12&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;Mkdir&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;F7&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;F7&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;Create New File with Vim&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;Shift-F4&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;Shift-F4&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;Edit File with Vi&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;F4 (See &lt;a href="http://www.cyberciti.biz/tips/midnightcommander-set-vi-as-default-editor-viewer.html"&gt;Use vi as Default Editor)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;F4 (need configuration)&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;View File&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;F3&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;F3&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;Copy File Name&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;M-w (See &lt;a href="https://www.midnight-commander.org/browser/misc/mc.keymap.emacs"&gt;mc.keymail.emacs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;No hotkey&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;Copy Full Path to CLI&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;C-S-Enter&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;Don't know&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;Directory History&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;M-h (actually history of all the commands&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="left"&gt;Don't know&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/tbody&gt; &lt;/table&gt;  &lt;/div&gt;</description><category>en</category><category>linux</category><category>mc</category><category>tc</category><guid>http://blog.binchen.org/posts/the-most-important-features-of-midnight-commander-mc/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 23 Jan 2012 08:29:00 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>